## Summary

Found bug: `numpy.f2py.crackfortran.markoutercomma` crashes with AssertionError on unbalanced parentheses. This causes f2py to fail ungracefully when parsing malformed Fortran code instead of providing helpful error messages. Bug report saved to `bug_report_numpy_f2py_markoutercomma_2025-08-18_04-58_la7s.md`.
